@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam packageStyle rect

actor "Logistics Operator" as LO
participant "System" as System

title SSD: Check and Select Missing Plans

LO -> System : Clicks "Check Missing Plans"
activate System

System -> System : Search for dates without saved plans
System --> LO : Show Modal with list of missing dates
deactivate System

LO -> System : Select a specific date from the list
activate System

System -> System : Update selected date in form
System -> System : Clear previous calculation results
System --> LO : Close modal and display date ready for computation
deactivate System

@enduml